        <p class="guide-sub">Investor financing across St. Pete, Clearwater, Dunedin, and Largo. Short-term rental income eligible. Condo programs available. No W-2 required.</p>
        <div class="guide-meta">
          <span class="guide-meta-item">Viador Partners, NMLS #2822744</span>
